Back to you Karice for follow-up...

See Bug 138425 for my explanation of the invalid locale issue. se is not the swedish locale - sv is (or sv_SE). I checked this with a valid Swedish locale and this is working fine.

Reducing to major.
fix is in ICU4J 3.4.5 which was released into the 3.2.1 build M20060830-0800. Also see bug 150296.
